<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10095404>
    dc:description "PLATE 1. Figures 1–8. Acusa, Tentasetae, Pseudobscura, and Parens species, adults. 1, Acusa acus, male holotype, Malaysia E, Borneo NE, Sabah; 2, Tentasetae cambodiana, male holotype, Cambodia, Prov. Kampot; 3, Pseudobscura karwaria, male holotype, India SW, Karwar; 4, 5, Parens occi (Fibiger & Kononenko, 2008), 4, female holotype, Russia, Far East and 5, male, paratype, S Korea; 6, P. paraocci, male holotype, Taiwan; 7, P. melli, female holotype, China, Fuk San; 8, P. chekiangi, male" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10095404/files/figure.png" ;
